00:19:23.170 --> 00:19:24.850
got the same puzzle.

00:19:24.850 --> 00:19:27.700
And Ivan says, I want
my cheese sandwich.

00:19:27.700 --> 00:19:29.687
Which sandwich is
he going to take?

00:19:29.687 --> 00:19:31.270
You think he's going
to take that one?

00:19:31.270 --> 00:19:32.510
Let's see what happens.

00:19:32.510 --> 00:19:33.670
Let's see what he does.

00:19:33.670 --> 00:19:37.240
Here comes Ivan, he says,
I want my cheese sandwich.

00:19:37.240 --> 00:19:39.730
And he takes this one.

00:19:39.730 --> 00:19:42.572
