00:19:49.460 --> 00:19:51.640
First, he predicts
Ivan will take

00:19:51.640 --> 00:19:54.040
the sandwich that's really his.

00:19:54.040 --> 00:19:57.460
And second, when he sees Ivan
taking the sandwich where

00:19:57.460 --> 00:20:00.310
he left his, where we would say
he's taking that one because he

00:20:00.310 --> 00:20:02.170
thinks it's his,
the three-year-old

00:20:02.170 --> 00:20:03.970
comes up with
