about the distinction

01:13:14.870 --> 01:13:17.000
between intentional
and accidental harm.

01:13:17.000 --> 01:13:19.500
And in ASDs, it doesn't.

01:13:19.500 --> 01:13:23.038
OK, that's probably just
one of a bunch of things

01:13:23.038 --> 01:13:24.330
that are going to be different.

01:13:24.330 --> 01:13:27.410
This is, as far as I know, the
only one that's been published.

01:13:27.410 --> 01:13:28.280
I see some squints.

01:13:28.280 --> 01:13:30.590
Are you not getting this, or do
