01:14:09.410 --> 01:14:12.240
so that you can do
the discrimination.

01:14:12.240 --> 01:14:14.640
You could do representational
similarity analysis,

01:14:14.640 --> 01:14:16.230
actually, come to think of it.

01:14:16.230 --> 01:14:19.490
Then, you wouldn't have to
have the whole dichotomy.

01:14:19.490 --> 01:14:21.350
That's interesting.

01:14:21.350 --> 01:14:23.850
OK, Heather, has
