01:14:23.850 --> 01:14:25.620
You're my informant here.

01:14:25.620 --> 01:14:26.520
You could take--

01:14:27.360 --> 01:14:33.900
OK, so Shash is
suggesting, why not

01:14:33.900 --> 01:14:36.490
ask this kind of question
of this standard localizer

01:14:36.490 --> 01:14:36.990
experiment?

01:14:36.990 --> 01:14:41.460
And I said, well, it wasn't set
up with an obvious dichotomy.

01:14:41.460 --> 01:14:44.130
And then I was
thinking, actually, you

01:14:44.130 --> 01:14:47.280
could take all of the
belief conditions,

01:14:47.280 --> 01:14:49.890
and you could do an RSA
on those in the ASDs

01:14:49.890 --> 01:14:52.860
and on the typicals, and ask if
their patterns are different.

01:14:52.860 --> 01:14:53.520
Right?

01:14:53.520 --> 01:14:55.562
I bet they've done that.

01:14:55.562 --> 01:14:57.410
See what I mean?

01:14:57.410 --> 01:15:00.560
Anyway, all right, I'll stop
